{
  "stem": "24171.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So in every house, the teacher was in that family house, room and board.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If there were two-- two children, they had to-- to do a double.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They figured it out between themselves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the most-- the boys were going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The girls were not-- they were-- the girls was like this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We get picked up, whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My girlfriend went to a special-- not special.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I mean, she had [? their ?] two brothers were kind of in the yeshiva.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "When they were home, they were teaching her [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Because they were kind of younger, she-- they were still at home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Well, when I was home, my brothers were not already.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They were-- well, one of them, which lived in Prague.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the other one was working away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I surprised my parents with a Hebrew reading.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Well, we had geese and things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So I used to go and mind the geese way out from the village.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because as I say, it's just kind of country life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I use to switch in the [INAUDIBLE], and my, whatever I took lunch.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I learned to read.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I surprised my parents one day when I knew how to read.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were very happy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's how it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Was there a synagogue or a beth midrash in the--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was just a beth midrash.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was kind of just one of the people had.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they just didn't have any children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had one son, kind of, grown up-- in my time, what I remember.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember something way before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he donated like half of the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He left for himself two bedrooms and the two of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
